				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok everyone,
<br />

<br />
List has been sent in and also posted on SoE Magician Definition board.
<br />

<br />
Special Thanks to:
<br />

<br />
shadowdirk,spitre,jiggs,bones5,abig99,sisko,arislaan,aariifrog
<br />
abonminatrix,naladini,kokuryu,silverblads,nicaruveq,syllence
<br />
sebbohnivlac,majestic,dalren,lildailye,stan,reanya,sympkynn
<br />
aadorna,rixsar,maston,kirium,nitim,belgerion,rotlom,qurrgoth
<br />
daybrighter2,zaniel,raura,xalmat,cyricus, djjinn, zarath,tsr,tulisin
<br />
eriol, qaedian, bemagi, eandori, sehra and anyone else I may have forgotten.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal">Magician Top Ten List</span>
<br />

<br />
1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">Improve pets</span> (new detail provided)
<br />
a)Damage ability (DPS upgrade, stats/hit consistancy + accuracy /damage crits)
<br />
b)Survivability/Defense upgrade (SVstats/Mitigation)
<br />
c)Utility (improved commands/procs/spells)
<br />
d)Fix our lvl 51 and higher fire pets
<br />

<br />
2. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Revamp pet focus availability/drop rates</span> (new request)
<br />
a)Summoners boon -Add quest version in tier 2 or equivalent zones
<br />
for those w/o LDON
<br />
b)Minion of darkenss - increase drop rate in Vex Thall, Add a quest in
<br />
the new Veeshans Peak. Add the focus to Teir 3 PoP mob drops,Ex:
<br />
First Sargents Insignia/Orb of Infinite Terror
<br />
c)Introduce the Mancy (MoE level) pet focus into the elemental planes
<br />
d)Increase drop rate of MoE
<br />
e) Or introduce pet focus quests/drops/augs in new OoW zones (tiers 1-6)  
<br />

<br />
3. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Fix GoD Nuke Imbalance</span> (new request)
<br />
This was caused from a missing GoD nuke. Mages were skipped for a GoD spell with a 20% increase to our highest damage nuke FoT. OoW nukes now have a 30% increase to the GoD nuke which we never got. Instead this 30% is being now applied to our old top damage nuke (FoT) 2K nuke, making our new OoW nuke 2600. Because this 30% is applied all nuking classes (including mages), Mages have now fallen far behind. This is should to be fixed. Our new OoW nuke should have 3120 damage (FoT2K + 20% in GoD=Missing bolt in GoD2.6K + 30% = BoJ 3120 in OoW), in order to keep us balanced and even with the other nuking classes. 
<br />

<br />
See this link:http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=magicianbalance&message.id=1756
<br />

<br />
4. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Improve pet heals</span> (new detail provided)
<br />
a)Shorter cast times, shorter recast times
<br />
b)HoT, quickheal, CH spell options
<br />
c)Have pet focus enhance pet heals
<br />
d)Increase heal amount
<br />

<br />
5. <span style="color: red"><span style="text-decoration: underline">Overhaul class specific AA's</span></span>, <span style="color: green"><span style="text-decoration: underline">AA cost reductions</span></span> and <span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline">Utility spells</span></span> (Updated request.. See bottom for detail)
<br />

<br />
6. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Update Rains</span> (new request)
<br />
Remove the innate resists on Rains, and retune the mana cost on many rains "See <a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/editorials/rains.html" target="_blank">http://www.magecompendium.com/editorials/rains.html</a> for
<br />
details".
<br />

<br />
7. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Allow pets to live while the master is invisible</span> (new request)
<br />
this will assist us on defense and will also allow us to use Eye of Tallon without killing pet. (changed because we were told no on suspended pets zoning)
<br />

<br />
8. <span style="text-decoration: underline">COH useable in more zones.</span>
<br />
Make CoTH available in all corpse summoning zones. If a small area
<br />
of the zone is necessary to have both coth/corpse summon blocked
<br />
for potential exploit reasons then just block that small area of the
<br />
zone.
<br />

<br />
9. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Upgrade our summoned items</span>. (updated request)
<br />
a)PC equipable items should have OoW era focuses, stats and resists.
<br />
b)Pet only items should have new procs like slow, snarelure and rune.
<br />
c)Mage summoned augs should be created
<br />

<br />
10. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Rathe's Son and the new OoW earth pet</span> (new request)
<br />
Remove the proximity aggro that root causes which makes our earth pet undesireable in groups and on raids. Possible solutions: 
<br />
a) Replace root with 100% snare which will remove proximity aggro but still have the same effect as root plus it will not break on nukes.
<br />
b) Re-code pet root with proximity aggro component removed.
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">PvP concerns</span>:
<br />

<br />
1 - <span style="text-decoration: underline">Make our pet's pvp targets -20% AC</span>
<br />

<br />
2 - <span style="text-decoration: underline">Treat pets *melee* damage as pvp melee damage and pet spell/proc damage as pvp *spell* damage</span>,
<br />

<br />
3 - <span style="text-decoration: underline">Have the separate durations for spells </span> such as snare and enthrall in pvp apply to our pets as well
<br />

<br />
See this link for detail: <a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/viewtopic.php?t=16550&highlight=" target="_blank">http://forum.magecompendium.com/viewtopic.php?t=16550&highlight=</a>
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">AA's</span>, <span style="color: green">AA cost reductions</span>and <span style="color: blue">Utility spells</span>detail from #5 above</span>
<br />

<br />
a)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Fix Elemental Agility</span></span>- this AA is broken please fix it. Reduce AA cost by 2/3rds.
<br />

<br />
b)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Fix Elemental Forms</span></span>- Remove the levi component from air form as this weakness (not being able to use Air Form in zones where levi is disabled) does not exist in any of the NPC's or pets in the game and therefore should not be a weakness for a PC.
<br />

<br />
c)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Fix Shared health</span></span>- increase range from contact to Line of sight
<br />

<br />
d)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Fix Mend Compainion</span></span>- Change this to a % heal of the pet's total buffed HP with 75% cap and add a 2nd level with 100% cap (it is currently level of the magician X 33+1)
<br />

<br />
e)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add new Quick Damage AA</span></span>
<br />

<br />
f)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add new Improved Damage Shield AA</span></span>
<br />

<br />
g)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add new Pet Convergence AA</span></span>- innate ability (forces pet to attack one target till target is dead) 
<br />

<br />
h)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add new Pet Control AA</span></span>- innate ability (allows master to move pet with arrow keys) Ex C+arrow
<br />

<br />
i)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Enhanced Frenzied Burnout</span></span>- 2-2.5 minute duration, add 2nd level Cleave 3 and 100% pet crits, add 3rd level Double Damage.
<br />

<br />
j)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Enhanced Host of Elements</span></span>- increase hp make SV immune. Add other elemental forms (water,fire,air)
<br />

<br />
k)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add Healing Adept and Gift, Advanced Healing Adept and Gift</span></span>
<br />

<br />
l)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: red">Add Elemental Fury Mastery</span></span>- have crits apply to spells
<br />

<br />
m)<span style="text-decoration: underline">Add Servant of Ro- 3 new levels</span>, SoR pet charges and explodes on mob for 4500, 5500, 6500 DD.
<br />

<br />
n)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: green">Secondary Forte</span></span>- lower cost from 15 to 10
<br />

<br />
o)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: green">Elemental Alacrity</span></span>- lower cost from 3/6/9/12/15 to 3/3/3/3/3
<br />

<br />
p)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: green">Refunds needed on Turned Summoned</span></span> remove this AA please
<br />

<br />
q)<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="color: blue">Add new mage spells-</span></span> Root, AE malosini, Group CoTH, Malos and Pet "kit" spells for targeted summons.
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">Requests removed from top ten</span>:
<br />

<br />
-Targeted summons (reason.. soon to be completed, developers are giving it to us prior to OoW)
<br />

<br />
-MGB (reason.. replaced with Improved DS AA)
<br />

<br />
-Quick MGB- (reason.. developers said not at this time)
<br />

<br />
